== 被收購 ==
2010年11月23日，Novell接受{{tsl|en|Attachmate|Attachmate|Attachmate公司}}以22億美元的收購要求。

2014年9月，[[大型主機|大型主機]]軟體公司[[Micro_Focus|Micro Focus]]宣布以12億美元收購Attachmate公司，包括 Novell<ref name="Jackson_MicroFocus">{{cite news |author-first=Joab |author-last=Jackson |title=Micro Focus buying Novell, Suse Linux owner for $1.2 billion |url=http://www.networkworld.com/article/2684353/micro-focus-buying-novell-suse-linux-owner-for-12-billion.html |access-date=2017-01-10 |archive-date=2022-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321190542/https://www.networkworld.com/article/2684353/micro-focus-buying-novell-suse-linux-owner-for-12-billion.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。收購於2014年11月20日結束，SUSE組織與Micro Focus內的前Novell組織其餘部分分開<ref name="PR_closed_2014">{{cite press release | url=https://www.attachmate.com/company/news/press/2014/micro-focus-international-completes-merger-with-the-attachmate-group.html | title=Micro Focus Completes Merger with the Attachmate Group | publisher=Attachmate Group | date=2014-11-20 | access-date=2021-11-10 | archive-date=2021-07-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210729083848/https://www.attachmate.com/company/news/press/2014/micro-focus-international-completes-merger-with-the-attachmate-group.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。SUSE於2019年被出售給 EQT Partners<ref name="SUSE acquired by EQT Partners">{{cite web|url=https://www.enterprisetimes.co.uk/2019/03/18/eqt-completes-aquisition-of-suse-from-micro-focus/|title=EQT completes aquisition [sic] of SUSE from Micro Focus|author=Ian Murphy|website=www.enterprisetimes.co.uk|date=2019-03-18|access-date=2020-05-02|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806010808/https://www.enterprisetimes.co.uk/2019/03/18/eqt-completes-aquisition-of-suse-from-micro-focus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Novell產品本身被重新命名並分散在Micro Focus的文件和網絡服務、協作和安全產品線中，例如Open Enterprise Server、GroupWise和Zenworks等Novell開發的產品被標榜為Micro Focus產品，但沒有提及它們在Novell時期的過往<ref name="MF_datasheets_2021">See for example the datasheets and other product documents for [https://www.microfocus.com/media/data-sheet/open_enterprise_server_2018_ds.pdf Open Enterprise Server] {{Wayback|url=https://www.microfocus.com/media/data-sheet/open_enterprise_server_2018_ds.pdf |date=20220303095327 }}, [https://www.microfocus.com/media/what's-new/groupwise-whats-new.pdf GroupWise] {{Wayback|url=https://www.microfocus.com/media/what%27s-new/groupwise-whats-new.pdf |date=20220120022942 }}, and [https://www.microfocus.com/media/data-sheet/zenworks_endpoint_security_management_data_sheet.pdf ZENworks] {{Wayback|url=https://www.microfocus.com/media/data-sheet/zenworks_endpoint_security_management_data_sheet.pdf |date=20220321185533 }} as accessed on the Micro Focus website on 2021-02-18.</ref>。

